    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Straightforward, budget-friendly, and priced to move, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for the right buyer. It shows clear signs of age and wear, but it remains a solid opportunity for someone seeking inexpensive transportation, a starter project, or a parts donor with real value. Offered transparently and represented honestly, this is a chance to buy at a compelling price from a seller committed to a fair, no-surprises experience.",
