    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone handy, a first-time buyer, or anyone needing simple transport without spending a fortune. It\u2019s being sold honestly and priced to move, with lots of potential as a daily runabout, backup car, or little project. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, this one could be just the ticket.",
